1. FLARE_F6 branch has been copied as CORFU branch.
2. The components are implemented in CIAO_FLARE/DAnCE/tests/CIAO/FTComponent
   Set $CIAO_ROOT to CIAO_FLARE root.
3. ReplicationManager and HostMonitor processes are implemented in $TAO_ROOT/orbsvcs/LWFT_Service
4. ReplicationManager, HostMonitor, and StateSynchronizationAgent libraries are implemented in $TAO_ROOT/orbsvcs/orbsvcs/LWFT
5. Deployment plans, scripts are in CORFU-experiment-Aug-6-2010.tar.gz
   The experiments in the group-failover directory are tested.
6. FTComponentServer is in the CIAO_FLARE branch (revision 84357). 
   CORFU directory has an appropriate svn:externals property, which should pull it in.
7. Use env.sh to setup your environment.
8. Use FLARE-F6 or FLARE-F6-Copy experiments on isislab.


